com.weather.airlock.sdk.ui

Class StreamsManagerActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • FragmentActivity
      • com.weather.airlock.sdk.ui.StreamsManagerActivity

  • public class StreamsManagerActivity
extends FragmentActivity
    The class contains UI logic which enables a dev user to specify which airlock configuration branch a device will be working with. The branch purpose is to override a master configuration.
